{
  "stem": "5644.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because after all, he was working with us for 15 or so years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was a little bit, at that time, nicely towards my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said to him that he's not happy and that he prepared to have it start off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But if father doesn't want to, it's bad, bad luck [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right aw-- that was a shortage immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the Germans walked into Warsaw, start immediately queues for bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yes, start immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People did stock.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why they made the shops empty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the people who did have shops start to hide their little bit of food and sell it slowly out for better prices.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, that's, that's nothing unusual in, in, in time of war, that something like that happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because after mine experience-- 75 years, I seen it-- that had happen in every country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If there's a war or starting a war, the food is the first thing to be hit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because that's the only thing which you can get some more money during wars than you get before the war [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't been with the family all the three weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because after few days, I been-- my brothers had been taken to the army, the older brothers, both of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was in the officer school before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one was just a university student which was taken immediately to the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish army.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And before the war-- in the start, in the start of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They have been taken to the army, both of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And mother was with me, with mine sister and younger brother that was the what left in, at home-- father, mother, and three children.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
